Summary: Fluidlike mettallic rolling cube shifted out of visual phase.
trends: There have been 20 other sightings in Santa Barbara
There were no other sightings in Santa Barbara on or around June 8th 2009
divs: Sighting Details setting: at the back porch and talking on the phone. a mettallic yet fluidlike cube seemed to be rolling at or slightly below marine layer height which, yesterday, was approximately 1800 ft. and just breaking up to typical afternoon sunshine, i.e. partly cloudy skies. the object appeared thumbnail-size which would suggest an actual size of a van or small house. the object was traveling wnw at a relatively slow rate of speed and seemed to shift out of visual phase as waves might cancel each other when out of phase (pardon my physics).
